{"tid":1961302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲研究：頭蝨藥能在48小時消滅武肺病毒","createTime":"2020-04-06T16:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T02:07:03.000Z","uid":28114,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d0e57d1c62521f8fe59b657f66b6e73bbd2553d9","tid":1961302,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/4/1586071218_jP-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F4%2F1586071218_jP-1280w.jpg&h=5c6c5edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n研究新冠肺炎的治療方案，各國其出奇謀。針對現有藥物的成效，繼法國的抗瘧疾藥研究和澳洲的卡介苗注射試驗後，最近澳洲蒙納殊大學一項小型研究發現，一種頭蝨藥竟然可以治療新冠肺炎。該結果已刊載於《Antiviral Research》(抗病毒研究)期刊，引起學界討論。<br />\n由大學Biomedicine Discovery Institute的Kylie Wagstaff博士所領導的研究，發現一種用來治療抗寄生蟲藥物的伊維菌素(Ivermectin)，只需單劑量便可在24小時有效減少新冠病毒的核糖核酸數量，博士更稱48小時內將病毒完全清除。伊維菌素早在1981年面世，廣泛用作治療頭蝨、線蟲感染等寄生蟲疾病。臨床使用的副作用包括皮膚灼熱感、乾燥和眼睛紅癢。<br />\nKylie Wagstaff博士指人體臨床試驗最快將在1個月內進行，由於未清楚入藥方法、劑量和實際藥效，民眾切勿自行購買服食，以構成危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.as.com/en/2020/04/04/other_sports/1586014265_026414.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.as.com%2Fen%2F2020%2F04%2F04%2Fother_sports%2F1586014265_026414.html&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lezcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=0894485a\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.as.com/en/2020/04/04/other_sports/1586014265_026414.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A0%AD%E8%9D%A8%E8%97%A5%E8%83%BD%E5%9C%A848%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E6%B6%88%E6%BB%85%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-214096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E8%259D%25A8%25E8%2597%25A5%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%259C%25A848%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%25BB%2585%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-214096&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lezcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=ae38d84c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A0%AD%E8%9D%A8%E8%97%A5%E8%83%BD%E5%9C%A848%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E6%B6%88%E6%BB%85%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-214096</a>"},{"pid":"5c96d98a6cd91d09cb5b2ba99a761d86c161b3fa","tid":1961302,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"照食都唔會有危險啦, 1 劑過<br />\n<br />\n0.4mg/kg body weight."},{"pid":"1d7334f95a9c3946954735cc7cca3a0694e7e0c2","tid":1961302,"uid":228868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a413ad541e23d5e9319c8a1cb051bb0f87f842d","tid":1961302,"uid":142067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d7334f95a9c3946954735cc7cca3a0694e7e0c2","tid":1961302,"uid":228868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:01:11.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"放到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"574234300f633a1dc3113f211c62b61803ca3e34","tid":1961302,"uid":254594,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:13:01.000Z","msg":"最近咁多新聞話現有藥物可治武肺<br />\n到底有幾多單係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n病毒感染幾時變得咁易醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23050bbb036d3e813d59ca03ccafe96dd2ab5146","tid":1961302,"uid":353701,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:18:40.