ote":{"pid":"574234300f633a1dc3113f211c62b61803ca3e34","tid":1961302,"uid":254594,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:13:01.000Z","msg":"最近咁多新聞話現有藥物可治武肺<br />\n到底有幾多單係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n病毒感染幾時變得咁易醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:48:04.000Z","msg":"1. 實驗室結果, 好多時同臨床結果有出入, 始終人體條件複雜好多<br />\n2. 實驗室環境, 唔需要考慮服用後的毒性, 可唔可以被人體吸收使用. 外用既藥, 同內服既藥, 注射既藥, 已經好唔同.<br />\n3. 現有結果可能只係一兩個病人既data, 可能只係好彩, 用係100個病人可能只有5個人有效, 其餘95人係無效. 咁即係無乜用.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以, 就算係現成藥物發現初步有效, 行完phase 3 clinical trial, 都有可能肥佬."},{"pid":"520aecd7eb4204be183af3478ac345a8a7251433","tid":1961302,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BODtgEC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBODtgEC.gif&h=7bf473e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e558633159712f74368a8fdcd59dc4c421603e3b","tid":1961302,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:00:04.000Z","msg":"屌你好痕呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bdb56ba656727dc36bec559fcee57f50b0f6c1","tid":1961302,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"574234300f633a1dc3113f211c62b61803ca3e34","tid":1961302,"uid":254594,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T17:13:01.000Z","msg":"最近咁多新聞話現有藥物可治武肺<br />\n到底有幾多單係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n病毒感染幾時變得咁易醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"因為死亡率 最多15%左右<br />\n<br />\n難聽少少咁講 <br />\n咩都唔做都有機會好<br />\n<br />\n甚至極端少少<br />\n<br />\n甚至可以得到用菜刀斬左隻手   <br />\n可以醫治武漢肺炎的怪論<br />\n<br />\n真正研究<br />\n要2組 甚至更多 (每組可能幾百人)<br />\n來 做對照實驗<br />\n<br />\n看下有無明顯的數據差異"}]}